A distance from the Traienrs abse, smoke streaks the sky as the 
Violator continues to fly. Insaide the ship Vile frantically presses 
buttons trying to get the transwarp gate device to activate. Soon the 
massive ship passes over Maximal city although the ship was still 
high in the sky. If any maximals were paying attention they could see 
the ship.. but only for a brief mintue or so for just as the ship got 
over the city the transwarp gate activated and the ship dissapeared...
(whee no they didnt leave the RP Im just jusing that so they can 
crash were their supposed to quicker).

Elsewhere, at the Trainer base battle, the shots fired at the 
Infecticon ship are all absorbed into its shield. Inside the Ship the 
leader of the Infecticon strike force looks to one of the massive 
energy beings before her.

Frostbite: "Hellpeon, we will be departing from this battle and 
heading to a secure location. I want to remain here and make sure 
that base is destroyed."

The being infront of Frostbite nods before a panel opens beneath the 
beast sending him flying down at high speeds. The shields around the 
Ifnecticon ship dissapear for a second as the Infecticon enforcer, 
Hellpeon speeds down to the ground and lands a short distance behind 
starscream, the impact forming a large crater beind the bot. Above, 
the Ifnecticon ship seemingly dissapears as it phase shifts. A moment 
later the ship heads off to find a secure area. As ths happens 
Hellpeon flys up out of the crater he had just made at high speeds 
and lands behind Starscream. Without a shred of warning the black 
energy beast gathers Chaochitan energy into its palms before 
launching a beam of it at starscream, as the beam travels the ground 
beneath it cracks and breaks from the force of it.
